\begin_layout Standard
The way in which crops are sold—cash-in-hand small quantities to itinerant
 traders—is equally problematic.
 It leads to a low bargaining power for the farmer and traders generally
 pass on transaction costs to smallholders 
\begin_inset CommandInset citation
